      • supportsVersionManagement

        public boolean supportsVersionManagement()
        Description copied from interface: Catalog
        Whether this catalog supports version management for tables. If not, corresponding methods will throw an UnsupportedOperationException, affect the following methods:
        • Catalog.commitSnapshot(Identifier, Snapshot, List).
        • Catalog.loadSnapshot(Identifier).
        • Catalog.rollbackTo(Identifier, Instant).
        • Catalog.createBranch(Identifier, String, String).
        • Catalog.dropBranch(Identifier, String).
        • Catalog.listBranches(Identifier).
        Specified by:
        supportsVersionManagement in interface Catalog
